ne><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>How does it influence learning?</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Transactional Learning: </strong>Pursuing stability often leads to a transactional approach to learning, where individuals focus solely on acquiring knowledge necessary to pass exams or meet job requirements rather than engaging in deep, meaningful learning experiences.</p></li><li><p><strong>Narrow Skillset: </strong>The narrow focus on stability-oriented careers may result in individuals developing a limited skill set, as they prioritise acquiring specific qualifications or competencies relevant to their chosen career path. Often these skills end up being quite dated and are not able to keep up with the changing times.</p><p></p></li></ul><h2>#3 Geography: &#8220;I want to work near my house.&#8221;&nbsp;</h2><p>Geography plays a significant role in career choices and learning opportunities. In a state like Gujarat, more people want to pursue entrepreneurship, whereas in Bihar, youth aspires for government jobs.&nbsp;</p><p>Geography is often a constraint for job selection as well. The COVID-19 pandemic caused trauma and fear among migrant workers and their families. Youth also prefers to work in their native language further causing them to be restricted by jobs in their states.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg" width="1456" height="1456" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1456,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;India in Pixels by Ashris on X: \&quot;Why India works? https://t.co/VLq1Alc1ob\&quot;  / X&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="India in Pixels by Ashris on X: &quot;Why India works? https://t.co/VLq1Alc1ob&quot;  / X" title="India in Pixels by Ashris on X: &quot;Why India works? https://t.co/VLq1Alc1ob&quot;  / X" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f35c2b4-c59a-4b93-ad99-a64aa07a4dc5_4096x4096.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/F7ALXRgXcAAyrah?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096">India in pixels by Ashris on X</a></figcaption></figure></div><h2>How does it influence learning?</h2><ul><li><p><strong>Limited access to learning opportunities: </strong>Geographical constraints limit individuals' access to educational resources, such as quality schools, libraries, and vocational training centres, thereby restricting their learning opportunities and career prospects.</p></li><li><p><strong>Restrictive curriculum: </strong>Educational institutions in remote areas offer limited curriculum choices, focusing primarily on traditional or vocational subjects aligned with local industries, which may not align with broader career aspirations or market demands.</p></li></ul><h2>#4 Proximity: &#8220;Like Sanjay Bhaiya&#8221;</h2><p>Individuals often base their career aspirations on the role models and opportunities available in their immediate surroundings. Friends, family &amp; their learning &amp; career choices are what influence people&#8217;s decision making - this further propagates the geographical pockets of careers &amp; learning preferences.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Despite the influence of media, personal interactions and local role models still carry significant weight in shaping career aspirations.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff4588449-ceed-40f0-a568-ef269805332d_800x600.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff4588449-ceed-40f0-a568-ef269805332d_800x600.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff4588449-ceed-40f0-a568-ef269805332d_800x600.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff4588449-ceed-40f0-a568-ef269805332d_800x600.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff4588449-ceed-40f0-a568-ef269805332d_800x600.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.